Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you’ve refused to allow\Nthe interrogation of the pilot of Unit 01,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one directly involved\Nin the incident, Major Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir. He is very unstable,\Nemotionally speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that it would be\Nunwise to have him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as his proxy, let us ask you,\NMajor Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,did the Angel not attempt to\Ncommunicate with us, mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I find no suggestion of that\Nin the subject’s report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is believed to have been an irregular incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming his memory is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no evidence that his memory\Nhas been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Eva’s AC recorder\Nwas not functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the Angel interested in the human psyche?\NIn the human mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am unable to answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the Angels even have\Na concept of what a mind is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether they can understand\Nhuman thoughts or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is completely unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident has a new element in it,\Nin that the Angel tried to take an Eva into itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any possibility that this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,may be linked to the predicted Thirteenth Angel\Nand all Angels thereafter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the pattern thus far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to suggest such a systematic\Norganization among the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! It is obvious that they have\Nworked independently, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not allowed to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be all. Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angels are beginning to attain intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The time left to us is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.66,Title Cards3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1227.204,689.917)}{\fs50}EPISODE 17\N{\fs65}THE FOURTH\NQUALIFIED\NINDIVIDUAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Running short?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient in Room 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergency room patient\Nfrom that E incident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s been hospitalized here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve heard her injuries are really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s still in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s here again today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he comes to see her\Nat least twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s a good and caring brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.89,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H88786F&\pos(652.012,240.583)}Suzuhara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.89,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&H967EAC&\pos(1012.68,341.333)}Empty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.89,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&H967EAC&\pos(623.084,482.25)}Empty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, boys like that are pretty rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, are you all right today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir. I will go see Dr. Akagi tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the day after I’ll be at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand! Bow! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today’s absences are the usual Ayanami,\Nand Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s up with Kensuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koike is also absent today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,New Yokosuka. Chasin’ battleships again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the class in modern Japanese\Nwill be self-study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship called Myoko, or somethin’\Nlike that, is in port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the student\Non duty today will be…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver the printouts to Ayanami after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, 1st Branch is okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the info from Satellite 5 immediately.\NIt’s top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the schedule for Unit 04 is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter, we’ll have the Magi evaluate\Nthe data discrepancies from the sensors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like confirmation on the synchro data\Nand the S2 engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll get rid of the noise over on our end.\NJust send us the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re sure the 2nd Branch just vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir, it’s been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Administration and Investigation\Ndepartments are going crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and General Affairs is in a total panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only clues are these\Ngeosynchronous satellite photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing else left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,10 seconds…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,8…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,7…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,6…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,5…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,4…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,3…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 04 and all related\Nresearch facilities within an 89km radius
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,have completely vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with several thousand people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the time schedule,\Nwe believe it to be an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,during the experimental installation of\Nthe S2 engine that was restored in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Potential causes range from
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a lack of structural integrity to\Na preliminary design stage error.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s 32,768 possibilities right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And there’s also the chance of sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn’t explode, it vanished, right?\NIn other words, it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In all probability, they were swallowed\Nby a Sea of Dirac,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,just like Unit 01 was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the S2 engine that we finally restored?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone. Our dream’s been shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what we get for trying to push ourselves\Ninto using something we don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for the Evas too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about the remaining Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re going to base it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the U.S. Government doesn’t\Nwant to lose the 1st Branch as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re the ones who insisted on\Nthe right to build Units 03 and 04.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they’re foisting just\Nthe dangerous parts off on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about self-serving bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After a disaster like that,\Nanyone would get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do\Nabout the activation test?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you use that dummy plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve still got to decide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the dummy plug prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei’s personal data has been loaded into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but it’s not really possible to digitize\Na human mind and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, it’s a fake, an imitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a machine that emulates\Na pilot’s thinking process.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll transmit a signal pattern to the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the Eva believes there’s a pilot\Nand synchronizes, that’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the data into Unit 01 and Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still some problems with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not important. As long as\Nthe Eva activates, it’s sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve delegated the transportation\Nof the Unit to the U.N.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It should arrive by the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll perform the modifications\Nand activation test in Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the test pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The dummy plug is still risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of our prospective candidates…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll select a fourth, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is one child whose core\Ncan be prepared immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, you can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand! Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch time! Lunch time! This is the\Nsingle best thing ’bout school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t bring lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t have time to cook last night\Nbecause of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you’re telling me to go without lunch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s this? Married couple fightin’ again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s all this formality for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the Unit 03 activation test at Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll be using the fourth as the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fourth Child’s been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven’t received a report\Nfrom the Marduk Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The official documents will be\Ndelivered tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Akagi, aren’t you hiding\Nsomething from me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay. So, who’s the selected kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the people, it’s that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All the candidates were gathered\Ntogether for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll be hard to break to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka will be fine. Her pride’s\Nriding on her piloting of the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rei is an exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing good comes of becoming\Ninvolved with us and the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji understands that better than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want him to suffer any more hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need children of this kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for us all to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the pure ideals,\Nis that what you’re saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara, you’re on duty this week,\Nso get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The printout!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency Evacuation Training\NEnforcement Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t our teacher tell you to deliver this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,C’mon, class rep, you can ask\Nthe other person on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ayanami is absent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Ayanami and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can’t exactly go to a girl’s place alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, I’ll go along…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk home with me, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami, we’re coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think it’s good to barge into\Na girl’s room without her permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She won’t see it if we leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a girl’s room? It’s so unwelcomin’.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,Notice\NClass News
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you shouldn’t touch anythin’!\NShe’ll get pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain’t helpin’!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not a man’s job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but Miss Misato hates guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care! It’s my policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw you,\NI really thought you were a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn’t seem like you’d\Ndo somethin’ for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it depends on\Nwhat you’ve got to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re visitin’!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the printouts that were pilin’ up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it upon myself to clean up a little.\NBut I didn’t touch anything except trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva pilots sure are weird, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Words of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Words I’ve never used.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d never even said them to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The city, a paradise made by mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Once driven from Paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,man had no choice but to escape to this\Nearthly existence, side by side with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,created by the resourcefulness that this\Nweakest of beings was forced to develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect ourselves from the fear of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to satiate our thirst for pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a paradise we created ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This city’s truly such a paradise.\NA armed city made to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A city of cowards fleeing from\Nthe outside world, filled with enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cowards do live longer. That’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo-3, Nerv’s camouflaged\Nintercept fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The continually-delayed seventh\Nconstruction phase will be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last, it will be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you report Unit 04’s accident\Nto the Committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the facts state, the cause is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this stage, it’s a catastrophic loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 04 and the 2nd Branch are acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the S2 engine,\Nwe may have lost the sample,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but we still have the data in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This installation and Unit 01 will be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Committee was furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was an unscheduled accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seele must also be frantically\Nadjusting the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidents not depicted in the\NDead Sea Scrolls can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This ought to teach the old men a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The intercept system here is finally\Ngoing to be completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and there isn’t even one measly party planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv sure is an uptight organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know how Commander Ikari is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll tell Miss Katsuragi and Dr. Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll cover up your mouth first…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So how’s work going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s going, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have work to do. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Far be it from me to comment\Non your private life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but would you keep your hands off\Nour young girls in this emergency situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t your jurisdiction, though, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I hit on you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on how you answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the secrets of Adam down there\Nand the Marduk Institute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking for help isn’t like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t afford to care right now.\NI don’t have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s behind the oh-so-convenient\Ndiscovery of the Fourth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marduk Institute doesn’t exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv itself is pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go check out Code 707.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,707?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji’s school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ritsuko wants to see you about\Nthe business trip you’re going on tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Wanna go out for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I’m a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you’d be a more\Nserious person, Mr. Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you’re comfortable around someone,\Nyou sure don’t hold back, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I’m sorry too. I didn’t mean\Nto sound sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I’ll show you something neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they watermelons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, aren’t they cute? This is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a secret from everybody else, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Making something…\NNurturing something is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see and learn so many things\Nfrom the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what’s enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And about suffering too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found anything that you enjoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But knowledge of suffering makes you\Nall the more capable of kindness to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that’s different from being weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She says they’re starting the synch test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.34,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fix the depth at 3.2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so. Shinji’s synch rate is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.47,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LCL thickness is nominal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.64,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Harmonics level is negative 1.1…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.67,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}0.5…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But something must have happened\Nduring that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.97,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}0.9…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.68,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}0.10…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something psychological.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.01,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Current exponent is 0.9.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it even harder to tell him\Nabout Unit 03’s pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.90,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All results posted to Melchior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pilot will be officially informed tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand! Attention! Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.76,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toji Suzuhara of Class 2-A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.50,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toji Suzuhara, report to the Principal’s Office.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothin’ comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:18:02.18,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\c&H7D706A&\pos(970.686,327)}Principal’s Office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I’m Toji Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re Toji Suzuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your trip to New Yokosuka yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Way cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I picked up\Nsome interesting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the one they were building in America.\NIt’s completed, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you’ve got to keep it a secret,\Nbut please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I really haven’t heard anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven’t you heard the rumor\Nthat the activation test
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,will be held at the second test facility\Nin Matsushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot hasn’t been chosen yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Miss Misato would pick me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji, would you ask her for me too?\NI want to be an Eva pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the story\Nthat Unit 04’s been lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don’t know about that either?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared along with the entire 2nd Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard my dad’s section was in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t heard anything from Miss Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it doesn’t concern\Npilots out on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If she didn’t tell you, it’s likely because\Nyou don’t need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about bothering you with weird questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But Toji sure is taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, we, mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,survived the hell on Earth called\Nthe Second Impact and rose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of children has\Nbeen decreasing yearly…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already heard. Take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it is you, the younger generation,\Nwho will lead the way to the future…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Toji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He’ll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s got class duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The school is now closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All students must go home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re on duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you line up the desks\Nand write up the daily record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t had lunch yet.\NI’ll do it as soon as I’ve eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara, you always buy your lunch\Nfrom the school co-op.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not like I’ve got anyone to cook for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:24.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two sisters, named Kodama and Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I always cook lunch for them, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I’m actually a good cook,\Nthough you might not think it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always end up cooking\Ntoo much for our lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need help gettin’ rid\Nof your leftovers, I’ll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,District 3 transformation test complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Asuka? Sorry, I’m a little busy\Nright now. Later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you make time for Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, not right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our synch data reports, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the hell is this? What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is HE the Fourth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don’t understand! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.64,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(947.727,778.5)}NERV 1st BRANCH, USA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.71,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1539.388,720)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.24,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 03 is delivered to Matsushiro\Nfrom America for the activation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unaware of the coming tragedy,\Npeople gloried in the last of their daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: “The Selection of Life”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.25,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,THE SELECTION OF LIFE
